		{
			x: 9.0d
			y: 8.5d
			subtitle: "Calling your horse. Left Click for more info"
			description: ["Simply sneak-right-click the Ocarina on an eligible entity will claim it, and the tooltip will now contain the name of the entity (according to your localisation), as well as the UUID of the entity. Repeating this will unclaim it; doing this to another entity will unclaim the original entity before claiming the new one.Right-clicking again at any time will attempt to summon the entity to you, even if that entity happens to be in an unloaded chunk. Should the chunk by unloaded, the Ocarina will attempt to load the chunk and summon the entity from it, and then the chunk will be unloaded again."]
			dependencies: ["153EBA0E05C07D6D"]
			id: "03E949BFB46103AD"
